            <div class="content">
             <p>
              <span style="line-height: 1.538em;">
               If you're ready for a physics program that combines exciting research topics with close faculty interaction, why wait? Apply today.
              </span>
             </p>
             <div class="alignLeft">
              <p>
               <a class="btn btn-theme btn-small pull-right" href="http://graduatedivision.ucmerced.edu/prospective-students/how-apply" target="_blank">
                Graduate Application
               </a>
              </p>
              <p>
